*Windows Key* + Space = Overview mode
*Windows Key* + Tab = Alt Tab for activities
Alt + Space = Search feature
KDE Connect = System settings 'KDE Connect' = Phone to laptop / sync / messages / lost phone noise / copy pics + videos
Activities = Schedule / Directories
Plasma Vaults = Click system tray (show hidden items) = Encryption passwords/files/pictures/documents






